item.title: Ip Ban Command Porblem
item.dc:creator: @grimreaper61 grimreaper61
item.description:
@grimreaper61 wrote:

with the delta source it is not BannedIps…its ipbans which means you probably leeched your ipban from another source. Change appendToBannedIps to p.writeLog(p.playerLastConnect, "ipbans"); p.disconnected = true; this will put there name and last ip in the ipbans file and kick them to confirm the ban.
